
* * *  PONG  - Public domain -  3/Jul/92
* * *  written by Claudio "PYRATRONIK" Buraglio of Italian Bad Boys (I.B.B.).


Keys:	F1	- Select Left  control (Mouse/Joystick/Paddle/Keyboard).
	F2	- Select Right control (Mouse/Joystick/Paddle/Keyboard).
	F10	- Change racket size (small/large).
	Del	- Reset score.
	Help	- Change color preset.
	Esc	- Quit.
	Space	- Change Game (Tennis/Hockey/Squash/Pelota).
	[	- Select color to change.
	]	- Select color to change.

  Left	Shift	- Left  racket Up.
  Left	Alt	- Left  racket Down.
   	Ctrl	- Start game.
  Right	Shift	- Right racket Up.
  Right	Alt	- Right racket Down.
	Return	- Start game.


Keypad:	+	- Increase ball speed.
	-	- Decrease ball speed.

	1	- Increase Blu.
	2	- Decrease Blu.
	3	- Set Blu to zero.
	4	- Increase Green.
	5	- Decrease Green.
	6	- Set Green to zero.
	7	- Increase Red.
	8	- Decrease Red.
	9	- Set Red to zero.

